The '''7th parallel north''' is a [[circle of latitude]] that is 7 [[degree (angle)|degrees]] [[true north|north]] of the [[Earth|Earth's]] [[equator|equatorial plane]]. It crosses [[Africa]], the [[Indian Ocean]], [[South Asia]], [[Southeast Asia]], the [[Pacific Ocean]], [[South America]] and the [[Atlantic Ocean]].

==Around the world==
